00:48:50.800 --> 00:48:55.700 position:56%
These are players that were declared
traitors because they left Cuba

00:48:55.700 --> 00:48:57.000
and suddenly they were able

00:48:57.000 --> 00:49:01.730
to travel back there freely
with this goodwill tour.

00:49:01.730 --> 00:49:05.200
You know and the Cuban
government, I mean if they wanted.

00:49:05.200 --> 00:49:07.820
If they want to save baseball in
Cuba they need to do something

00:49:07.820 --> 00:49:11.250
to stop the defections or
have more control over this

00:49:11.250 --> 00:49:15.080
because that's what's been
hurting baseball there.

00:49:15.080 --> 00:49:16.690
And if they can come
up with a system

00:49:16.690 --> 00:49:20.430
where they can control
the players or which,

00:49:20.430 --> 00:49:23.170 position:56%
