to be some sort of a restriction

00:49:23.170 --> 00:49:25.600
on anybody who defects
actually playing then.

00:49:25.600 --> 00:49:27.470
I don't know how that
would work out either so,

00:49:27.470 --> 00:49:31.230
there's a lot of questions but I
do think that it's just a matter

00:49:31.230 --> 00:49:33.530
of time before we do see it.

